data.description: Welcome to Lost Colony Drive, a beautiful property spanning over 4 acres in New Kent, offerinng unparalleled privacy and tranquility. Beyond its picturesque setting, what truly distinguishes this property is its detached three-car garage featuring a spacious two-bedroom apartment above, offering remarkable versatility. The main house features an additional attached two-car garage, with four bedrooms, two and a half baths including a convenient first-floor primary suite. You'll also find a cozy kitchen, formal living and dining areas, and a family room with cathedral ceilings and a double-sided brick fireplace. Venture into the backyard to discover an inviting in-ground pool nestled discreetly behind the house, providing an ideal space for relaxation and leisure. Conveniently located near restaurants, shops and schools, this property is a must-see for those seeking convenience and country living!
